## V3: Dashboard Navigation & Analytics
The app has undergone a major UX layout shift from a single page configuration to a full Dashboard design with Sidebar navigation.

*   **Difficulty-Weighted Scheduling**: Subjects are added as individual rows, allowing users to define difficulty weights (Easy/Medium/Hard). Hard subjects are allocated three times the amount of days as Easy subjects, improving study priority management.
*   **Progress Tracking**: Users can mark generated days as "Completed" via checkboxes. Total study compliance is shown as a percentage bar in the Progress tab.
*   **Analytics Engine**: An analytics tab combs through historical study data from `localStorage` to compute a completion rate. If a user drops below 50% for a scheduled subject, a dynamic "Weak Subject Warning" is displayed to encourage corrective action.

