## V5: Attendance Tracker (RVR & JC Regulations)
The latest update adds a specialized tracker for classroom attendance, following RVR & JC College of Engineering standards.

*   **Semester-Wise Subjects**: Select your semester to automatically load the RVR & JC curriculum subjects (Sem 1 to Sem 8).
*   **75% Threshold Warning**: The app calculates your attendance percentage in real-time. If it falls below the mandatory 75%, a red "LOW" warning is displayed.
*   **Total Persistence**: Like the GPA and Planner, your attendance logs are saved locally for every semester.

![Attendance Tracker View](/home/sudheendra/.gemini/antigravity/brain/184136d7-5a09-4648-92bf-6d4eff22a34a/attendance_tracker_records_1771763029784.png)

